OL,3,C'This is for killing our children':
OL,4,CMan recalls words of synagogue attacker
OL,6,FA man who helped to barricade the
OL,7,Fdoors of a synagogue during Thursday's
OL,8,Fattack in Manchester has said he heard
OL,9,Fthe attacker shout "this is what they
OL,10,Fget for killing our children", while
OL,11,Ftrying to get through the doors.
OL,13,FAlan Levy was worshipping at Heaton
OL,14,FPark Hebrew Congregation Synagogue in
OL,15,FCrumpsall, Greater Manchester, when
OL,16,FJihad Al-Shamie, 35, drove into a
OL,17,Fgroup of people outside before
OL,18,Fattempting to enter the building.
