OL,3,C'This is for killing our children':
OL,4,CMan recalls words of synagogue attacker
OL,6,FTwo men were killed outside the
OL,7,Fsynagogue, on the holiest day of the
OL,8,FJewish calendar. They have been named
OL,9,Fby police as 53-year-old Adrian Daulby
OL,10,Fand 66-year-old Melvin Cravitz. Three
OL,11,Fothers remain in hospital with serious
OL,12,Finjuries.
OL,14,FMr Levy described how he saw Al-Shamie
OL,15,Fwaving a knife, and ran inside the
OL,16,Fsynagogue to tell the congregation
OL,17,Fwhat was happening.
