OL,3,C'This is for killing our children':
OL,4,CMan recalls words of synagogue attacker
OL,6,FAs he helped to barricade the doors,
OL,7,Fhe says he saw Al-Shamie "with a big
OL,8,Fknife, banging his knife into the
OL,9,Fglass, trying to get through".
OL,11,F"The heroes of the congregation who
OL,12,Fsaw what was happening then came to
OL,13,Fthe doors because he was trying to
OL,14,Fbreak the doors down to get in.
OL,16,F"We were barricading the doors between
OL,17,Fus with Rabbi Walker and a number of
OL,18,Fthe other congregants. He couldn't get
OL,19,Fin because we were holding the doors
OL,20,Ffirm."
