OL,3,C'This is for killing our children':
OL,4,CMan recalls words of synagogue attacker
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News UK Editor Paul
OL,7,FBrand, Mr Levy said he heard the
OL,8,Fattacker shout "this is what they get
OL,9,Ffor killing our children".
OL,11,F"All I heard him say was when the guys
OL,12,Fwere outside the perimeter and were
OL,13,Fshouting at him. He shouted "this is
OL,14,Fwhat you get for killing our children."
