OL,3,C'This is for killing our children':
OL,4,CMan recalls words of synagogue attacker
OL,6,F"It's just truly horrific," Mr Levy
OL,7,Fsaid. "The attacks against our
OL,8,Fcommunity. Our children aren't safe in
OL,9,Fschools, we have to have guards. Our
OL,10,Fpeople are not safe at the synagogue
OL,11,Fgoing to pray on the holiest day of
OL,12,Four year."
OL,14,FThe attacker, 35-year-old Jihad Al-
OL,15,FShamie, was shot dead by police seven
OL,16,Fminutes after officers were alerted to
OL,17,Fthe attack.
