OL,3,C'This is for killing our children':
OL,4,CMan recalls words of synagogue attacker
OL,6,FIn a statement on Friday, the Chief
OL,7,FConstable of Greater Manchester Police
OL,8,Fsaid one of the victims of the attack
OL,9,Fsuffered a wound consistent with a
OL,10,Fgunshot injury, while another is in
OL,11,Fhospital also having suffered a
OL,12,Fgunshot wound.
